info.author: Seneca Cunningham
info.description: Allows a script to create a menu based user interface that can be easily set to, and properly display in, multiple environments.  Currently multiui has curses, gtk2, and plain text output capabilities.
info.name: multiui
info.summary: python package with a common API for different output methods
